nodes.text: Feytihennasraof was one of three Elders of the Oswaft species in 3 BBY. Fey objected at first to Lando Calrissian's plan for Oswaft to create false images of themselves by excreting heavy metals, but was eventually won to the idea and participated in the Battle of ThonBoka. Feytihennasraof survived the guns of the Imperial Fleet, but was slain by Rokur Gepta's electromagnetic torpedo.
Fey's gender is never specifically mentioned, but Lando once calls the Elder 'Sir'.
